{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "一个大L等于一个分数，上面是1下面是N，然后乘一个大大的求和符号。求和符号下面写着T从1开始，上面写着N。求和符号后面跟着一个括号，括号里面是字母gamma T减去一个头上戴帽子的gamma T，最后整个括号外面有个小小的2，表示平方。", "output": "L = \\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{T=1}^{N} (\\gamma_{T} - \\hat{\\gamma}_{T})^2", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Mean Squared Error", "category": "stats_ml", "sympy_expr": "Eq(L, 1*Sum((-\\hat{\\gamma}_T + gamma_T)**2, (T, 1, N))/N)", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "商法则那个，x over phi 的导数，就是 x prime times phi 减去 x times phi prime，整个 over phi squared。", "output": "\\left(\\frac{x}{\\phi}\\right)' = \\frac{x'\\phi - x\\phi'}{\\phi^2}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Quotient Rule", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(transpose(x)/transpose(phi), (phi*transpose(x) - x*transpose(phi))/(phi**2))", "perspective": "researcher", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "CE loss L，就是负的1 over N，然后sum over m from 1 to N。里面是xi m 乘以 log xi hat m，再加上 (1 减 xi m) 乘以 log (1 减 xi hat m) 的形式。", "output": "\\mathcal{L} = -\\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{m=1}^{N} \\xi_{m} \\log(\\hat{\\xi}_{m}) + (1 - \\xi_{m}) \\log(1 - \\hat{\\xi}_{m})", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Cross-Entropy Loss", "category": "stats_ml", "sympy_expr": "Eq(L, (1 - xi_m)*log(1 - \\hat{\\xi}_m, 10) - 1*1*Sum(xi_m*log(\\hat{\\xi}_m, 10), (m, 1, N))/N)", "perspective": "researcher", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
