{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "curl(B_vec) == mu_0 * J_vec + mu_0 * epsilon_0 * d_E_vec_dT", "output": "\\nabla \\times \\mathbf{B} = \\mu_0 \\mathbf{J} + \\mu_0 \\varepsilon_0 \\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{E}}{\\partial T}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Ampere-Maxwell Law", "category": "physics", "sympy_expr": null, "perspective": "programmer", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "一个括号里面，上面是x，下面是像个圈带一竖的符号，整个括号外面右上角有个小撇。然后等于号右边，上面是一个减法。减号前面是x带个小撇，乘以那个圈带一竖的符号。减号后面是x，乘以那个圈带一竖的符号带个小撇。最下面是那个圈带一竖的符号，然后整个再平方。", "output": "\\left(\\frac{x}{\\phi}\\right)' = \\frac{x'\\phi - x\\phi'}{\\phi^2}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Quotient Rule", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(transpose(x)/transpose(phi), (phi*transpose(x) - x*transpose(phi))/(phi**2))", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "左边是一个字母H，右下角跟着一个T。它等于一个叫'tanh'的函数，括号里面有三部分相加。第一部分是字母W乘以字母X，X的右下角也跟着一个T。加上第二部分是字母U乘以字母H，H的右下角是T再减一。最后再单独加上一个字母B。", "output": "\\mathbf{h}_{T} = \\tanh(\\mathbf{W}\\mathbf{x}_{T} + \\mathbf{U}\\mathbf{h}_{T-1} + \\mathbf{b})", "metadata": {"formula_name": "RNN Hidden State Update", "category": "stats_ml", "sympy_expr": "Eq(h_T, tanh(U*h_{T-1} + W*x_T + b))", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "L = -1.0 / N * SUM(m=1..N, xi_m * log(xi_hat_m) + (1.0 - xi_m) * log(1.0 - xi_hat_m))", "output": "\\mathcal{L} = -\\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{m=1}^{N} \\xi_{m} \\log(\\hat{\\xi}_{m}) + (1 - \\xi_{m}) \\log(1 - \\hat{\\xi}_{m})", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Cross-Entropy Loss", "category": "stats_ml", "sympy_expr": "Eq(L, (1 - xi_m)*log(1 - \\hat{\\xi}_m, 10) - 1*1*Sum(xi_m*log(\\hat{\\xi}_m, 10), (m, 1, N))/N)", "perspective": "programmer", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "J 等于一个方框框，里面有四块。第一行是“f1”对“y1”的小弯弯除法，旁边是“f1”对“y2”的小弯弯除法。第二行是“f2”对“y1”的小弯弯除法，旁边是“f2”对“y2”的小弯弯除法。", "output": "J = \\begin{bmatrix} \\frac{\\partial f_1}{\\partial y_1} & \\frac{\\partial f_1}{\\partial y_2} \\\\ \\frac{\\partial f_2}{\\partial y_1} & \\frac{\\partial f_2}{\\partial y_2} \\end{bmatrix}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Jacobian Matrix", "category": "matrix", "sympy_expr": null, "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "d/dz [f(g(z))] == f_prime(g(z)) * g_prime(z)", "output": "\\frac{d}{dz} [f(g(z))] = f'(g(z)) g'(z)", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Chain Rule", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(Derivative(f*g(z), z), z*g(z)*transpose(f)*transpose(g))", "perspective": "programmer", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "H(f) = [ [ d2f/dg1^2, d2f/(dg1*dg2) ], [ d2f/(dg2*dg1), d2f/dg2^2 ] ]", "output": "H(f) = \\begin{bmatrix} \\frac{\\partial^2 f}{\\partial \\gamma_1^2} & \\frac{\\partial^2 f}{\\partial \\gamma_1 \\partial \\gamma_2} \\\\ \\frac{\\partial^2 f}{\\partial \\gamma_2 \\partial \\gamma_1} & \\frac{\\partial^2 f}{\\partial \\gamma_2^2} \\end{bmatrix}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Hessian Matrix", "category": "matrix", "sympy_expr": null, "perspective": "programmer", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "就是三个分数连起来，第一个分数上面是sin字母A，下面是小a；第二个分数上面是sin字母B，下面是小b；第三个分数上面是sin字母C，下面是小c，这三个分数都相等。", "output": "\\frac{\\sin A}{a} = \\frac{\\sin B}{b} = \\frac{\\sin C}{c}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Law of Sines", "category": "algebra_trig", "sympy_expr": null, "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "L 等于 1 over N times sum from T=1 to N of (theta_T 减去 hat_theta_T) 的平方", "output": "L = \\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{T=1}^{N} (\\theta_{T} - \\hat{\\theta}_{T})^2", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Mean Squared Error", "category": "stats_ml", "sympy_expr": "Eq(L, 1*Sum((-\\hat{\\theta}_T + theta_T)**2, (T, 1, N))/N)", "perspective": "researcher", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "左边是cos，括号里面是数字2乘以一个像小w的符号。右边是cos，括号里面是那个小w，然后cos的右上角有个小2；再减去sin，括号里面是那个小w，然后sin的右上角也有个小2。两边用等号连起来。", "output": "\\cos(2 \\omega) = \\cos^2 \\omega - \\sin^2 \\omega", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Double Angle Formula", "category": "algebra_trig", "sympy_expr": "Eq(cos(2*omega), -sin(omega)**2 + cos(omega)**2)", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "左边是一个字母f，然后括号里有一个像小辫子的y。接着是一个等号。等号右边是一个大大的像躺着的M一样的符号，它下面写着k等于0，上面写着无穷大的符号。这个大符号后面跟着一个分数。分数的上面是字母f，f的右上角有个小括号里面是k，再后面括号里是字母a。分数的下面是字母k，k后面跟着一个感叹号。分数后面紧接着又是一个括号，里面是那个小辫子y减去字母a，整个括号的右上角有一个小k。", "output": "f(\\gamma) = \\sum_{k=0}^{\\infty} \\frac{f^{(k)}(a)}{k!} (\\gamma - a)^{k}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Taylor Series", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(f(gamma), Sum((-a + gamma)**k*f(a)**k/factorial(k), (k, 0, oo)))", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "h_k update 就是 tanh(W x_k + U h_{k-1} + b) 这种形式", "output": "\\mathbf{h}_{k} = \\tanh(\\mathbf{W}\\mathbf{x}_{k} + \\mathbf{U}\\mathbf{h}_{k-1} + \\mathbf{b})", "metadata": {"formula_name": "RNN Hidden State Update", "category": "stats_ml", "sympy_expr": "Eq(h_k, tanh(U*h_{k-1} + W*x_k + b))", "perspective": "researcher", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "左边是d，下面是dz，然后后面跟着一个中括号，中括号里面是f，f的括号里又套了一个g，g的括号里是z。等号右边是一个带一撇的f，f的括号里是g，g的括号里是z，然后这个整体再乘以一个带一撇的g，g的括号里是z。", "output": "\\frac{d}{dz} [f(g(z))] = f'(g(z)) g'(z)", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Chain Rule", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(Derivative(f*g(z), z), z*g(z)*transpose(f)*transpose(g))", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "一个长长的弯弯的符号，下面写着一个躺着的8，上面也写着一个躺着的8。接着是字母e，e的右上角是负号，然后是一个圈圈字母的平方。再后面是小写字母d，跟着那个圈圈字母。最后是等号，等号后面是一个勾勾里面装着像两根棍子中间一横的符号。", "output": "\\int_{-\\infty}^{\\infty} e^{-\\theta^2} d\\theta = \\sqrt{\\pi}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Gaussian Integral", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(Integral(exp(-theta**2), (theta, -oo, oo)), sqrt(pi))", "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "一个大写的F，等于一个下面带小写e的K，再乘以一个分数，分数上面是两个Q，一个Q下面带小1，另一个Q下面带小2，分数下面是一个大写的R，上面有个小小的2。", "output": "F = k_e \\frac{q_1 q_2}{R^2}", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Coulomb's Law", "category": "physics", "sympy_expr": null, "perspective": "beginner", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
{"instruction": "请将以下含糊、口语化或程序化描述还原为标准的 LaTeX 公式。", "input": "int f(theta) d_theta from a to b, 结果就是 F(b) 减 F(a) 嘛", "output": "\\int_{a}^{b} f(\\theta) d\\theta = F(b) - F(a)", "metadata": {"formula_name": "Fundamental Theorem of Calculus", "category": "calculus", "sympy_expr": "Eq(Integral(f(theta), (theta, a, b)), -F(a) + F(b))", "perspective": "researcher", "generator": "GeminiGenerator", "generator_model": "gemini-2.5-flash"}}
